\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">你越弱，佢越輕鬆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對呢啲言論，可以試吓咁諗：<br />\n和理非？2014年雨傘佔足三個月，大前日百萬行，結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好升級？尋日無升級，咪一樣開槍打頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再搞入暴動？而家777已經定性咗係暴動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bbd79ccdc3d3e5ad8592b46d67d4ee208bba328b","tid":1213173,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"我比較想行雷，五雷轟頂班黑警"},{"pid":"dbaf48cde9345982770711da7373cb47a642b41f","tid":1213173,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3fa29cb9ad67908428ef023ac99d3b2e52941f4","tid":1213173,"uid":21260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:52:52.000Z","msg":"真係好大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd6765518dcca60bf297f82a91982d2a0f6f65f","tid":1213173,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"唔落雨就出另一招<br />\n(如再開槍) 用鷹粟粉封技<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1213222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1213222</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"721080892904b03c1ef29a30af611d7d851459e6","tid":1213173,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"